description:
The Best of Simon Furman compiles material that spans 20 years, including material from the Marvel UK era and Furman's transfer to the Marvel U.S. book, as well as a few stories from Generation 2. Furman's return to Transformers after an 8-year gap is represented by his Dreamwave inclusions. Three stories from his current run with IDW are also represented.

Collects

  • Marvel Comics' Marvel UK #81, 86, 172–173
  • Marvel Comics' The Transformers #62, 70-71, 75
  • Marvel Comics' Generation 2 #7-8
  • Dreamwave Productions' The War Within Preview
  • Dreamwave Productions' Armada #16
  • IDW Publishing's The Transformers: Infiltration #6
  • IDW Publishing's Spotlight: Shockwave
  • IDW Publishing's Beast Wars: The Gathering #1

description: A perfect jumping-on point, featuring the cast of the summer blockbuster - but in Marvel Universe continuity! When the brand-new Zodiac rears its many heads, the Avengers must assemble to combat them. But who is behind the group's return? None other than Thanos, the mad Titan, who has claimed Earth as his own! The Avengers team up with cosmic blockbusters the Guardians of the Galaxy to bring Thanos some cosmically-charged pain ... but can even these two mighty teams stop Thanos from making Earth into the throneworld of his new empire? This explosive battle will change one of the Avengers' lives - forever! Brought to you by Marvel architect Brian Michael Bendis!
